- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): This sub-category covers topics related to computer vision, including self-supervised learning and image classification. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): This sub-category covers topics related to artificial intelligence, including transfer learning and domain adaptation.
